org.cpsolver.ifs.example.jobshop

Class Machine

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.model.Constraint<Operation,Location>
      • org.cpsolver.ifs.example.jobshop.Machine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Constraint<Operation,Location>>

    public class Machine
extends Constraint<Operation,Location>
    Machine constraint.

    Each machine contians a given set of operations (variables). A machine constraint is satisfied, if all operations on it do not overlap in time.
    Version:
    IFS 1.3 (Iterative Forward Search)
